.TH SIMPLE_SHELL 1 "Simple Shell" "Holberton School"
.SH NAME
simple_shell \- a simple UNIX command interpreter

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hsh

.SH DESCRIPTION
simple_shell is a basic UNIX command line interpreter.
It reads commands from standard input and executes them.

The shell can be used in interactive mode or non-interactive mode.

.SH OPTIONS
No command line options are supported.

.SH USAGE
Interactive mode:

.RS
./hsh
.RE

Non-interactive mode:

.RS
echo "ls" | ./hsh
.RE

.SH AUTHORS
Sajed, Ronan, Lonie
